{"tid":1605432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國民權抗爭老將的疑問","createTime":"2019-09-30T09:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:58:09.000Z","uid":325861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc66f59b560dd4f3e247ddc9f19bad4269d3790d","tid":1605432,"uid":325861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:42:42.000Z","msg":"鍾祖康引述法國民權抗爭老將朋友的疑問: <br />\n&quot;又跟民權抗爭老將的法國朋友聊天，當然論及香港的反送中運動，朋友說，看到香港警察一身造價不菲的裝備，頭部更用非常堅固的頭盔完全包裹，鐵甲人一樣，非常安全。<br />\n<br />\n但他說，非常奇怪，香港的抗爭者竟然不會向這些防暴警頭盔的保護鏡投擲任何顏料，個個防暴警的頭盔保護鏡竟然一塵不染。他說，投擲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">顏料</span></span>相當容易，而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">保護鏡一旦看不清，就要把保護鏡拉起，甚至要卸下頭盔，自衛能力就大減，或要以真面目示人</span>。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100000019477500/posts/2816086308401991?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100000019477500%2Fposts%2F2816086308401991%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=8bb75f25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100000019477500/posts/2816086308401991?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"e6f6fb55c4c2b8d1a09d653c354681e6a2bd7e15","tid":1605432,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:43:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4bc93178de5022b6695f215883be7cf13ab189c","tid":1605432,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:45:02.000Z","msg":"大YX + 黑油 PARTY"},{"pid":"bff4a091e27c53286de0d026666e0c2a76538742","tid":1605432,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"99b21122460ad8a677bb10de21c1aa3007ce0c0e","tid":1605432,"uid":99209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:58:09.000Z","msg":"不了，我地出黎係為左逃跑"}]}